name: react-demo
description: - Start webpack dev server with `npm run dev` - Use state to control an input - Create a child component and pass it props - Add a button that toggle a state variable - Add a conditional render - Change the style of something with a state variable - Add proxy to package.json, restart - Make a network call to get some data from an express server - Build with `npm run build` - Add static serving with express - Deploy and run on aws
